              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/15776756/" class="">第36页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fengpengzi/" class=" " title="劉道瓌">劉道瓌</a>
                (博學而篤志，切問而近思)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="15776756">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">《紀要》引蘇秦、范雎、荀況、田肯、張儀、蘇厲、國子諸子之言，論七國形勢。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-12-12 10:18</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                《紀要》引蘇秦、范雎、荀況、田肯、張儀、蘇厲、國子諸子之言，論七國形勢。
